Finite space…

…means choices matter.

If space, attention, memory, or symbols are bounded, compression becomes valuable. Patterns matter because you cannot carry everything. Humor matters because it carries disproportionate meaning in little space. Myth works because finite minds compress vast things into stories.

And from some of your recurring frames:

Finite space creates selection.
Selection creates pattern.
Pattern creates meaning.
Meaning propagates.

Or the quieter version:

Infinite space stores everything.
Finite space creates wisdom.